{"tid":2368961,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM發錢寒 又推出新男團 只限18歲及以下","createTime":"2021-01-16T16:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T17:17:51.000Z","uid":320858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0d5f4f7b5c68307dcb6a6d38928a3607e2dbe3","tid":2368961,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"SM Entertainment 今天（16 日）公開了《2021 SM NEW BOY GROUP AUDITION》的活動海報，將從即日起到 3 月 31 日間召募新男團的候選成員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVs3fB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVs3fB4.jpg&h=93401300&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTtU6JL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTtU6JL.jpg&h=f399e0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旗下只要是出生於 2002～2008 年間的男性，無論身在什麼地方，只要於 2 月 15 日前上傳能展現歌唱、舞蹈、個人特長⋯⋯等藝人潛力的內容即可報名，入選者需於 3 月 15 日前在韓、美、日、中等國的 SM 公司進行現場徵選。<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果成功入選 3 月 31 日公布的名單，未來就有機會成為 SM Entertainment 新男團的一員。"},{"pid":"282c63edeb110f07b30a1e09a8d98833fc0018f2","tid":2368961,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"NCT YOUNG 💘✊🏼"}]}